<p>
<note n="0137002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0137002">具＋（足）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0138001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0138001">唯＝惟【宮】</note>
<note n="0138002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0138002">唯＝惟【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0138003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0138003">唯＝惟【明】，【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0138004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0138004">非＝作【三】</note>
<note n="0138005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0138005">姓＝類【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0138006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0138006">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note n="0139001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0139001">茶＝荼【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0139002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0139002">斷＋（斷）【三】【宮】</note>
